overview: The user aimed to enhance a sleep questionnaire application by adding
  persistent data storage and an administrative interface. The agent evaluated
  the existing codebase, identified gaps, and developed a plan to integrate a
  PostgreSQL database using Prisma for questionnaire responses. A key part of
  the implementation was building a simple admin dashboard for data viewing and
  CSV export, protected by a password-based authentication system. Initially, a
  custom session management was implemented, but it was later refined to
  leverage Next.js middleware for a simpler and more efficient route protection
  mechanism. Comprehensive testing confirmed that all database operations, API
  endpoints, and authentication flows were fully functional, providing a robust
  solution for the client's requirements.
